pageContext.claim: “You saw what happened in Mexico, where they [the migrant caravan] came through the troops, and they hurt the troops. Tough people. They hurt the troops. They were throwing rocks at 'em. They were doing a lot of things, and they burst through the police and the troops in Mexico.”
pageContext.analysis: There was a skirmish at the Mexican border, but these comments are an exaggeration. A few Mexican police officers were injured, and reports suggest those injuries were not serious.
